</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="14" type="reference_group">
<paragraph pageId="3" pageNumber="14">
<taxonomicName class="Malacostraca" family="Sphaeromatidae" genus="Exosphaeroma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Exosphaeroma" order="Isopoda" pageId="3" pageNumber="14" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Exosphaeroma</taxonomicName>
Stebbing, 1900: 553, Restricted synonymy. - 
<bibRefCitation author="Bruce, NL" journalOrPublisher="Memoirs of Museum Victoria" pageId="31" pageNumber="42" pagination="309 - 369" title="New genera and species of sphaeromatid isopod crustaceans from Australian marine coastal waters." volume="60" year="2003">Bruce 2003</bibRefCitation>
