</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="14" type="type species">
<paragraph pageId="3" pageNumber="14">Type species.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="3" pageNumber="14">
<taxonomicName class="Malacostraca" family="Sphaeromatidae" genus="Sphaeroma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Sphaeroma gigas" order="Isopoda" pageId="3" pageNumber="14" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gigas">Sphaeroma gigas</taxonomicName>
Leach, 1818; by original designation (
<bibRefCitation author="Stebbing, TRR" journalOrPublisher="Proceedings of the General Meetings for Scientific Business of the Zoological Society of London" pageId="35" pageNumber="46" pagination="517 - 568" title="On some crustaceans from the Falkland Islands, collected by Mr. Rupert Vallentin." volume="1900" year="1900">Stebbing 1900</bibRefCitation>
